            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="Re:War is "cheap", occupation is expensive"><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>Re:War is "cheap", occupation is expensive<span> (0)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><span class="author" title="author name and user ID">Anonymous Coward</span> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3596889&cid=43317681">(#43317681)</a></h4>
