            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~wonkey_monkey" class="author" title="author name and user ID">wonkey_monkey (2592601) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3596889&cid=43317889">(#43317889)</a></h4>
