    <div id="comment_43319701">
        <header data-points="2" data-reason="Normal">
            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="As the submitter of this posting..."><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>As the submitter of this posting...<span> (2)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~mpthompson" class="author" title="author name and user ID">mpthompson (457482) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3596889&cid=43319701">(#43319701)</a></h4>
